# 📄 Document Q&A Bot using RAG

## 📌 Project Overview

This project is a simple Document Question Answering (Q&A) system built using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG). It allows users to ask questions based on the contents of a PDF document. The application retrieves relevant information from the document and displays the answer through a simple Streamlit interface.

---

## 🚀 Features Implemented

- ✅ PDF document processing
- ✅ Text extraction from PDF files
- ✅ Chunking and storing document data in ChromaDB
- ✅ Semantic similarity search
- ✅ Question answering through command line
- ✅ Streamlit-based user interface
- ⏳ Gemini-powered answer generation (In Progress)
- ⏳ Source citations (Future Enhancement)
- ⏳ Multi-document support (Future Enhancement)

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python 3.11
- Streamlit
- ChromaDB
- PyPDF
- Google Gemini API
- python-dotenv

